    "description": "The Italian for 'rags', stracci are torn, loosely cut or broken pasta. You'll break up lasagne sheets for yours, then cook in a creamy cherry tomato and crab sauce. Serve with a charred Tenderstem and almond salad. Crab it while you can.",
